sequenceDiagram
  participant U as Operator
  participant C as CLI parser
  participant R as research command
  participant O as orchestrator
  participant P as YouTubePipeline
  participant S as Services
  participant T as Technologies
  participant D as Data directory
  U->>C: srp research youtube TOPIC PURPOSES
  C->>R: argparse Namespace
  R->>R: parse platform, topic, purposes
  R->>O: ParsedRunResearch
  O->>P: PipelineState
  P->>S: stage service batches
  S->>T: technology execute calls
  T-->>S: TechResult output or None
  S-->>P: ServiceResult
  P->>D: reports exports sqlite cache
  P-->>O: state.outputs.report
  O-->>R: report dictionary
  R-->>U: report path
